   1:src/main.cpp  **** /**
   2:src/main.cpp  ****  * mpr121_synth.cpp ŌĆö Glass Touch Moog Synth
   3:src/main.cpp  ****  * Daisy Seed ŌĆö Bit-Bang I2C  SDA=D12  SCL=D11
   4:src/main.cpp  ****  *
   5:src/main.cpp  ****  * FINGER 1:
   6:src/main.cpp  ****  *   Position  ŌåÆ Pitch (quantized on touch-down, continuous slide after)
   7:src/main.cpp  ****  *   Pressure  ŌåÆ Filter cutoff (light=dark/closed, hard=bright/open)
   8:src/main.cpp  ****  *               + Vibrato depth (press harder for more wobble)
   9:src/main.cpp  ****  *
  10:src/main.cpp  ****  * FINGER 2:
  11:src/main.cpp  ****  *   Position  ŌåÆ Oscillator detune (spread between osc1 and osc2)
  12:src/main.cpp  ****  *   Pressure  ŌåÆ Wavefold distortion (gentle saturation to complex fold)
  13:src/main.cpp  ****  *               + Ring mod amount (extreme pressure adds metallic edge)
  14:src/main.cpp  ****  *
  15:src/main.cpp  ****  * EXPRESSION:
ARM GAS  /var/folders/1t/pyvz513s4fs9l00kxmc709xh0000gp/T//ccgY3Zif.s 			page 9


  16:src/main.cpp  ****  *   - Note quantize on initial touch, then free pitch bend on slide
  17:src/main.cpp  ****  *   - Pressure-controlled vibrato (LFO depth from finger 1 pressure)
  18:src/main.cpp  ****  *   - Portamento / glide between quantized notes
  19:src/main.cpp  ****  *   - Sub oscillator one octave below (adds weight)
  20:src/main.cpp  ****  *   - Soft-clip waveshaper before output
  21:src/main.cpp  ****  *   - Amplitude envelope: fast attack, pressure-controlled release
  22:src/main.cpp  ****  */
  23:src/main.cpp  **** 
